  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4d54e6da169902b4db8e974e80a3fe1a, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day 1 Radio Transmission
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  mandatory: 1
  lines:
  - ALERT TO ALL CITIZENS
  - As of a few moments ago, we have confirmed the arrival of an otherworldly presence
    enveloping the surroundings of the dome.
  - "We are yet to understand it\u2019s full capabilities, but have identified it
    contains a virus exposed individuals may be affected by."
  - The only currently known complication of this virus is a rash on either arm.
    Citizens who experience this complication must contact us via their computer
    messaging application immediately.
  - As of this moment, efforts are in progress to evacuate all citizens to a temporary
    safe location until this issue is resolved, alongside precautions in place to
    prevent exterior interference from governing figures of greater territories.
  - Information regarding such can be found on your computer messages.
  - To fulfil the evacuation, all citizens are instructed to not leave their home
    without proper authorization.
  - I REPEAT, CITIZENS MAY NOT LEAVE THEIR HOME WITHOUT PROPER AUTHORIZATION.
